--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> Firestrikes blade scraped against Menasor's thick armor. Menasor 
felt
> that, and for a second forgot where he was. Instinctivly he held
> Slaughter strongly with one hand, but he now had another attacker, 
he
> made a large backhanding motion with the hand that was being sliced 
by
> Firestrike, to send the Decepticon realing.
> 
> Megatron had lost interest for a minute, he nodded to Shockwave, and
> mentioned that they would be in touch, as he left.

::DOMNIJOE AND BLINDCHAOS::

    Domnijoe watched the happenings with grim amusement. 
    "There's always one in every crowd" she said to herself. She 
pulled her Lazer Sabre out of her subspace pocket and poised herself 
for a potential confrontation. She had an inkling things would get 
messy.
    Blindchaos's eyes twinkled with laughter. Internally he hoped 
Firestrike would reallt tick Menasor off and Megatron would let 
Blindchaos play with his left overs....if anything remained when he 
was done. The triple changer's grin became as bright as his stare, but 
only Domnijoe would have recognized the sadistic glow to his eyes.

Northlight
Domnijoe Productions
